# Tool editor UX & sitewide face uplift

Companion to [`responsive-layouts.mdc`](responsive-layouts.mdc) (shell tiers). This rule owns **editor chrome**, **face uplift**, and the **public-page register**.

## Hard rule: no tag-only refactors

Reject changes that only swap `py-12` → `py-8 md:py-12` without changing composition. Spot-check **375 / 768 / 1280 / 1536** — each must look intentional (columns, measure, CTA wrap, no page-level horizontal scroll).

## Layout contracts

| Kind | Contract |
|------|----------|
| Canvas tools | [`ToolEditorLayout`](src/components/tools/ToolEditorLayout.tsx): title `text-2xl md:text-3xl`, subtitle `mt-1`, form `Card density="compact"`, sticky preview `lg:sticky lg:top-4`, mobile Edit/Preview tabs ≥44px |
| Dual preview | `preview` + `previewSecondary` (board-banner) |
| Galleries | `belowGrid` (resizer all-formats) |
| Sources | `footer` slot — not a sibling ad-hoc PageShell |
| Non-canvas tools | densify only; no fake Edit/Preview |
| Guides | `GuideLayout` `py-8 md:py-12`; left-accent sections; Callout for notes; related-links row |
| Focus prose | `PageShell focus`; section dividers / Callout — not nested Cards for short prose |
| Header | `<lg` drawer; `lg+` existing Learn/Tools dropdowns (keep groups — see `comms-public-nav.mdc`) |
| Footer | wrap/stack; tap targets ≥44px |
| Auth | centered `max-w-md`; dense form; calm shell |
| Hub chrome | HubNav collapses under `md`; list pages dense; table scroll inside wrappers only |

## Face-uplift checklist (every page)

1. **Hierarchy** — one H1; section labels `text-sm font-medium text-gray-700`
2. **Controls** — `SegControl` for pill groups (`min-h-11`); selects share Input border/`min-h-11`
3. **Density** — Card `density="compact"`; form `space-y-3`; tool padding `py-6 md:py-8 lg:py-10`
4. **Touch** — primary actions and tabs ≥44×44; icon-only → Tooltip / aria-label
5. **Focus** — `focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-opseu-blue/40`
6. **Preview chrome** — screen `p-4 md:p-6` (not export `p-10`); sticky while editing
7. **Brand** — Brand Kit colours where chrome shows brand; no new OPSEU hex in core UI
8. **A11y** — radiogroup/`aria-checked` or `aria-pressed`; UndoRedoBar uses i18n `editHistory`
9. **Overflow** — no page horizontal scroll at 375
10. **Empty surfaces** — no orphan Cards; prefer Callout for short notes

## Shared primitives

- [`ToolEditorLayout`](src/components/tools/ToolEditorLayout.tsx)
- [`SegControl`](src/components/tools/SegControl.tsx)
- [`Tooltip`](src/components/tools/Tooltip.tsx)
- Card `density="compact"` | `"default"`

